 background give a character?', 'Two.']\n['BACKGROUNDS', 'What happens if a character would already gain the same skill proficiency from their class, lineage, or heritage features?', 'They can choose a different skill proficiency instead.']\n['BACKGROUNDS', 'What additional proficiencies or languages do most backgrounds grant?', 'Proficiency with one or more tools or the ability to learn additional languages.']\n['BACKGROUNDS', 'What equipment does each background provide?', 'A package of starting equipment.']\n['BACKGROUNDS', 'What is a talent, and how does a background allow a character to choose one?', 'A talent is a special ability that a character can choose from a short list of options provided by their background.']\n['BACKGROUNDS', 'What is an adventuring motivation, and how does a background help determine it?', \"An adventuring motivation is a reason why a character becomes an adventurer. A background contains suggested motivations to help inform the character's reasons for adventuring.\"]\n['ADHERENT', 'What is an Adherent background, and what does it represent?', 'An Adherent background represents a character who has devoted themselves to furthering a singular focus in their life, such as a faith, belief, or cause.']\n['ADHERENT', 'What skill proficiencies does an Adherent background provide?', 'Choose two from History, Investigation, Religion, or Persuasion.']\n['ADHERENT', 'What additional proficiencies does an Adherent background grant?', \"Proficiency with calligrapher's supplies and one type of tool or instrument of the character's choice.\"]\n['ADHERENT', 'What equipment does an Adherent background provide?', 'A prayer book or ceremonial dagger, a reliquary (holy symbol), a block of fragrant incense, vestments, a set of common clothes, and a pouch containing 10 gp.']\n['ADHERENT', 'What talent can an Adherent character choose from?', 'Field Medic, Mental Fortitude, or Ritualist.']\n['ADHERENT', 'What are some adventuring motivations for an Adherent